Rewards Schema:

- Provide functionality for redeeming rewards when the sufficient number of points are collected, and these points will come off the total of the user when spent.
  £5 off next purchase
  10% off next purchase
  £20 off next purchase
  25% off next purchase
  £50 off next purchase

-Consecutive green purchases result in a streak multiplier for green score points
  3 consecutive green purchases in a row activates this 

-Consecutive red purchases result in a penalty on green score points and rewards
  2 consecutive red purchases in row 

-Leaderboard prize for top ponts total

Extras: 
Rewards for specific spending categroies
Admin page for admin to set own rewards and possibly challenges
